<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>{{ article.title }} | AI・クラウド ニュースダイジェスト</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="../static/style.css">
</head>
<body class="article-page" style="--accent:{{ section.accent }}">
<header class="site-header">
  <div class="header-inner">
    <a class="back-link" href="../index.html">← ダイジェスト一覧へ</a>
  </div>
</header>

<main class="container article-container">
  <div class="article-meta">
    <span class="card-tag" style="background:{{ section.accent }}">{{ section.name }}</span>
    <span class="article-date">{{ article.published_date }}</span>
  </div>
  <h1 class="article-title">{{ article.title_html }}</h1>

  <div class="three-block" style="border-color:{{ section.accent }}">
    <h2 class="three-block-head">3行でわかる！今日のニュース</h2>
    <ul>
      {% for line in article.three_lines_html %}<li>{{ line }}</li>{% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="summary-pair">
    <p class="sum-ja">{{ article.summary_ja }}</p>
    <p class="sum-en">{{ article.summary_en }}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="article-body">
    {{ article.body_html }}
  </div>

  {% if article.references %}
  <div class="references">
    <h2 class="ref-head">▼ 関連リンク / References</h2>
    <ol>
      {% for ref in article.references %}
      <li id="ref-{{ ref.id }}">
        <a href="{{ ref.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{{ ref.title or ref.url }}</a>
        {% if ref.source %}<span class="ref-source">— {{ ref.source }}</span>{% endif %}
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ol>
  </div>
  {% endif %}
</main>

<footer class="site-footer">
  <p>本記事は複数の公開情報を基にAIが作成したオリジナルの日本語解説です。引用元の原文は上記リンクをご参照ください。</p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
